title: Beelzebub-jou no Okinimesu mama. (As Miss Beelzebub Likes.)
synopsis: According to legend, Beelzebub, one of the seven princes of Hell, betrayed God and was banished from Heaven for eternity. Beelzebub now leads the kingdom of Pandemonium, where all former angels roam and work every single day of their immortal lives.
